BuildRoot:	%{tmpdir}/%{name}-%{version}-root-%(id -u -n)

%description
GTK HTML Widget for the GNOME 2 platform.

%description -l pl
Widget GTK HTML dla platformy GNOME2.

%package devel
Summary:	Header files for GTK HTML 2
Summary(pl):	Pliki nag³ówkowe GTK HTML 2
